Niɣd '''Tagmart n ismḍal''' {{Tifinaɣ|('''ⵜⴰⵎⵖⴰⵔⵜ ⵏ ⵉⵙⵎⴹⴰⵍⵏ''')}}
Tunsift ad ar tsawal f tasrdunt niɣ tad n wayyis . Mac ɣid ar nsawal f yat tamɣart lli ɣ tinfusin n ufgan amaziɣ lli ibul ,w-akkuc acku ur tkn lḥqns. Tamɣart n ismḍal tkkis timlsit ns tumlilt lli igan tin taguḍi d umṭṭ f urgaz ns lli ittuymḍaln. (Dar imaziɣn urd timlsit tasggant ad igan tin taguḍi mac tumlilt). Tamɣartad lli f iṣxṭ wakkuc ar is grawl ɣ tuẓẓumin n yiḍ iskr gis tasrdunt n ismḍaln ..
